{"author":{"id":"cff9ab1d2ee9741039b2a60d90cca378a5320ba753398f6f3df8d03abcebee1b"},"ops":[{"type":1,"timestamp":1770887472,"nonce":"QLU3RXdy4hSuhDXkhT20FRf/3x8=","title":"Improve Leihvertrag: print CSS, PDF download, email to borrower","message":"The Leihvertrag (lending agreement) print experience is broken/poor:\n\n1. **Print CSS is missing/broken** - The printable agreement renders using a separate layout (app/views/layouts/print.html.erb) that references printable_agreement.css, but the output looks awful. Print styles need proper formatting.\n\n2. **Auto-opens print dialog** - Clicking 'Drucken' immediately triggers window.print() via a hidden iframe (app/views/lending/show.html.erb:92-96). There's no preview or option to download instead.\n\n3. **No PDF download** - The agreement should be downloadable as a PDF file.\n\n4. **No email to borrower** - The agreement should optionally be emailed to the borrower (depends on ActionMailer being configured, see git-bug cc7f2a6).\n\n**Affected files:**\n- app/views/lending/printable_agreement.html.erb (agreement template)\n- app/views/layouts/print.html.erb (print layout)\n- app/views/lending/show.html.erb:88-96 (print trigger via hidden iframe)\n- app/views/shared/_flash.html.erb:13-18 (auto-print on checkout completion)\n- app/controllers/lending_controller.rb:58-66 (show_printable_agreement action)\n- app/assets/stylesheets/ (missing print stylesheet)","files":null}]}